%MACRO { x ( x ) x }
%MACRO { x (x x ) x }
%MACRO { x (x x )x ) x }
%MACRO { x (x) x )x()() x ) x }
%MACRO { x (x) x)X )x()() x ) x }
%MACRO { x (
    BRK LIT2kr @label/label &sublabel
    .label #12 #abcd $1 |100 ~lib.tal
    "string [ ]
) x }

%MACRO { X( x )X ) x }

( Nested comments )
%MACRO { x ( x ( x ) x ) x }
%MACRO { x (x x ( x ) x ) x }
%MACRO { x ( x ( x )x x ) x ) x }
%MACRO { x (x x ( x )x x ) x ) x }
%MACRO { x ( x ( x ( x ) x ) x ) x }

( Not nested -- inner comment has other characters after the `(` )
%MACRO { x ( x (x x ) x ) x }
%MACRO { x (x x (x x ) x ) x }
%MACRO { x (x x (x )x ) x } x
%MACRO { x (x x (x x ) x } x

( Unclosed comments )
%MACRO { x ( x } x
%MACRO { x (x x } x
%MACRO { x (x ( x ) x } x

( Nested macros )
%MACRO { x ( x %NESTED x ) x } x ( Nested macro definition gets highlighted )
%MACRO { x ( x ( x %NESTED x ) x ) x } x
%MACRO { x ( x %NESTED { x } x

( Macros in comments )
x ( x %MACRO { x } x ) x
x ( } ) x
